title: #LiveOutside2016 Experience 360º Sunrise Over Rio
description: It doesn’t get much better than watching the sun rise over Sugarloaf Mountain from Mirante Dona Maria in Rio de Janeiro. Experience the moment by using the YouTube app to see it in 360, or by clicking and dragging on desktop using Chrome.
